{
  "texts": [
    "AI exhibits particular proficiency in image analysis, especially in the context of disease diagnosis through image evaluation.",
    "Its intrinsic resilience to fatigue and continual learning capabilities contribute significantly to its success, even surpassing the abilities of clinical professionals in this specialized domain [10].",
    "Nevertheless, AI's diagnostic accomplishments are dependent upon human clinicians who establish diagnostic criteria grounded in their own extensive practical experience.",
    "AI relies on human experts to guide its predictions, since it lacks the autonomy to independently interpret data or yield substantial and meaningful results [11].",
    "The relationship between AI and human users underscores the indissoluble connection between advanced AI and its clinical relevance."
  ]
}